<subSubSection pageId="52" pageNumber="536" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="52.[1444,2649,278,467]" pageId="52" pageNumber="536">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1445,1793,278,307]" pageId="52" pageNumber="536">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. The Manu Short-tailed Bat might have a wider distribution than is currently known. It occurs in some protected areas in south-eastern 
<collectingCountry box="[1988,2056,357,386]" name="Peru" pageId="52" pageNumber="536">Peru</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
